Program: The Documentary
Title: Interview with President Santos
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0492f9j
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 26 Sep 2016
The Colombian President Juan Manuel Santos is preparing to sign an historic peace deal with the Farc rebels to end five decades of war. President Santos speaks to the BBC's Lyse Doucet about the long road to peace. (Photo: President of Colombia Juan Manuel Santos speaks during a bilateral meeting with US President Barack Obama, 2016. Credit: Drew Angerer/EPA) Show less